com.yworks.yfiles.graph.styles

Class TemplateStripeStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.styles.AbstractTemplateStyle<IStripe>
      • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.styles.TemplateStripeStyle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IStripeStyle, ICloneable, Cloneable

    public class TemplateStripeStyle
extends AbstractTemplateStyle<IStripe>
implements IStripeStyle
    An IStripeStyle implementation that can render complex Nodes for the visualization of IStripes using a TemplateStripeStyleRenderer.

    This style implementation provides the ability to use the control templating mechanism to create the rendering for stripes. The StyleResourceKey is used to determine the Style that will be applied to the Node. The style will be looked-up in the CanvasControls the style is used in.
